sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Scheduler
    participant TripService

    Note over Scheduler,TripService: Nadejście terminu rozpoczęcia

    Scheduler->>TripService: StartTripScheduleTriggered
    TripService-->>Scheduler: TripStatusChangedToOngoing

    Note over Scheduler,TripService: Upływ terminu zakończenia

    Scheduler->>TripService: CompleteTripScheduleTriggered
    TripService-->>Scheduler: TripStatusChangedToCompleted